The 2.0 feature list is complete. These are the to-do items for version 2.1

- Add mouse-and-keyboard support (passthrough for PC games and emulation for console)
- Add support for XBox and DualSense controllers (passthrough or emulation)
- Allow mod choice to be restricted by group for voting candidates
- Edit config files in the UI
- Write counter/disgnostic output suitable for an OBS source
- Manage command permissions through interface
- Commands to configure game settings without UI
- Assign permissions to moderators as a group
